{"tid":870020,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【氣象】（2018年10月下旬）旬初高空反氣旋為廣東帶來晴朗天氣；東北季候風會於旬末抵達華南沿岸，天氣逐漸轉涼","createTime":"2018-10-20T17:38:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-27T06:34:16.000Z","uid":44630,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"43d665b5201aa937be6bfe7f5bc6a9924776ca21","tid":870020,"uid":44630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T17:38:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: brown;\"><img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/http://imgur.com/hBEht4a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FhBEht4a.png&h=4c32fde0&s={SIZE}\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>氣象討論：2018年10月下旬</ins></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">此帖文討論期：2018年10月21日至31日</span></span></strong><br />\n【註】 氣象討論帖一般逢每月1日、11日及21日發出新帖文。　當新帖文發出後，或有颱風追擊帖發出，原有的氣象討論帖會隨即停用。　為使大家有一個良好舒適的瀏覽環境，請不要使用簡體中文貼文、提及力場或洗版，謝謝合作。<br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">氣象台專頁現已登場</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://x.co/FBlike\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2FFBlike&h=5fdd3157&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"http://fb.com/HKGweather\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2FHKGweather&d=6QwtPriUDP2xM9PYNmK9OW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=9dda8db5\" target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/HKGweather</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://x.co/TWlike\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2FTWlike&h=e9b064ef&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"http://twitter.com/HKGweather\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKGweather&d=6QwtPriUDP2xM9PYNmK9OW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=89e8772c\" target=\"_blank\">http://twitter.com/HKGweather</a></span></em><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/BZfpfrS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FBZfpfrS.png&h=9df3da65&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"http://youtube.com/HKGweather\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2FHKGweather&d=6QwtPriUDP2xM9PYNmK9OW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=261977bb\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtube.com/HKGweather</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>◤參考資料</ins></span></span><br />\n◆ 實時天氣照片：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/ts/index_webcam_uc.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fwxinfo%2Fts%2Findex_webcam_uc.htm&d=6QwtPriUDP2xM9PYNmK9OW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=5feabc75\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/ts/index_webcam_uc.htm</a><br />\n◆ 天氣雷達圖像：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/radars/radarc_range1.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fwxinfo%2Fradars%2Fradarc_range1.htm&d=6QwtPriUDP2xM9PYNmK9OW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=32444932\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/radars/radarc_range1.htm</a><br />\n◆ 機場天氣預報：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/aviat/taf_decode.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Faviat%2Ftaf_decode.htm&d=6QwtPriUDP2xM9PYNmK9OW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=0c69a9c5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/aviat/taf_decode.htm</a><br />\n◆ 認識天氣現象：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/education/edu01met_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Feducation%2Fedu01met_c.htm&d=6QwtPriUDP2xM9PYNmK9OW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=95470546\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/education/edu01met_c.htm</a><br />\n◆ 各類天氣術語：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/flw_description/flw_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fwxinfo%2Fcurrwx%2Fflw_description%2Fflw_c.htm&d=6QwtPriUDP2xM9PYNmK9OW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=d68688a5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/flw_description/flw_c.htm</a><br />\n◆ 各類警告定義：